@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title EditUser Command Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant EditUserCommand
participant Ui
participant User as UserSingleton
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: edituser FIELD
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: EditUserCommand
Resumake -> EditUserCommand: execute(list)
EditUserCommand -> UserSingleton: getInstance()
EditUserCommand -> Ui: prompt new value
EditUserCommand -> UserSingleton: editField(field, value)
EditUserCommand -> Ui: show updated value
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
